Newton.Rufus Estabrook House:
The Rufus Estabrook House is a historic house at 33 Woodland Road in Newton, Massachusetts.


== Description and history ==
It is a 2-1/2 story wood frame structure, two bays in width, with a front-facing gable roof and a porch extending across the frontm supported by Ionic columns. The entrance is flanked by sidelight windows and wide pilasters.
